His Excellency, The Former Senator Representing Kaduna, Comrade Shehu Sani made this statement on his Facebook page after the hearing of Nnamdi kanu’s case in court.
Sani Said and I qoute “. My Brother Nnamdi, now that you have won One billion Naira, remember those of us who are not insulting you. When you are out, I’ll tell you the names of all those open and hidden enemies.
However, His reactions was followed after the court has awarded the sum of one billion naira damage to be paid to Nnamdi Kanu by the federal government over the invasion of his house.
According to the judge, the defence counsel who is the FG did little or nothing to defend the evidence as provided by the plaintiff.
What is your take on the Sani’s statement?


